{"tid":39471,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞][認真歌] 《毋忘我》、《忘我》","createTime":"2016-12-14T14:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T09:35:09.000Z","uid":45011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60753ba1e3602f61ed168c19f0e631e25f7ccdd9","tid":39471,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:52:51.000Z","msg":"上年Juno隻碟令好多人留意上下集既歌詞，其實小弟都寫過唔少既上下集歌詞，今次SHARE一下2008年寫既《毋忘我》(改自 何韻詩 願我可以學會放低你)，同埋2011年寫既《忘我》(改自何韻詩 鋼鐵是怎樣煉成的)，歌詞內容我相信都寫得好淺白，唔多講喇，去歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上集:<br />\n<br />\n《毋忘我》<br />\n原曲:何韻詩 - 願我可以學會放低你<br />\n作曲:徐偉賢<br />\n填詞:黃偉文 <br />\n改編歌詞:a仔<br />\n<br />\n熱愛的卻又遠觀   投入到發現從未結伴<br />\n但你偏好亦要管   何事你突然另結新歡<br />\n自尊心都經已賠本   縱使心胸都有幾尺寬<br />\n我始終   有不滿   仇恨都一概注滿<br />\n<br />\n如若我已清楚   錯在勇氣不多<br />\n太內向了因此遺禍<br />\n期待變了生疏   你仍賜我寶座<br />\n如落花枯萎也結成福果<br />\n<br />\n*下秒請你亦要記得我<br />\n  道別了仍然能掛念   怎麼不可<br />\n  念在我跟你曾經在此相識過<br />\n  每天跟你   總會是同坐<br />\n  下秒請你別要抹走我<br />\n  若下個與你還有另一點不妥<br />\n  就在這刻你難過   亦都可珍惜我<br />\n  遊歷過風霜也無阻<br />\n  你一失意   空虛那陣時   可否想我*<br />\n<br />\n其實我已清楚   結局太過坎坷<br />\n我才會狂想怎留座<br />\n寧願變作花朵   跌入你那寶座<br />\n難道花圃給你永恆封鎖<br />\n<br />\nRepeat *<br />\n<br />\n我只想你   貪新厭舊時   偷偷想我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下集:<br />\n<br />\n《忘我》<br />\n原曲: 何韻詩 - 鋼鐵是怎樣煉成的<br />\n作曲: Vincent Chow<br />\n填詞: 黃偉文<br />\n改編歌詞: a仔<br />\n<br />\n從來仍沒有高攀的志向   也自覺很正常<br />\n何以去想   最終的下場<br />\n<br />\n誰料到會擠身這競技場   屢敗屢戰誰想<br />\n怎受創傷   仍毫無保障<br />\n<br />\n文明裡太多天災加上戰禍令我   又敗下一仗<br />\n你與誰成雙   極平常   我比不上<br />\n<br />\n我慶幸這一生以後毫無顧慮   何用領受你允許<br />\n我怎麼可以往後退   等救援隊<br />\n若被困重災區   毅然不衰<br />\n<br />\n我要為此犧牲你為何流眼淚   何用你為我讚許<br />\n沒有掌聲如雷   只有洪水<br />\n在浸沒廢墟中   一些過去<br />\n<br />\n無名無氏世間怎麼記載   我踏過這舞台<br />\n誰會看出   箇中的精彩<br />\n<br />\n人沒法把先天基因刪改   青海與愛琴海<br />\n依然常在   誰人能不愛<br />\n<br />\n其實我已經一心一意奮力綻放但亦是青苔<br />\n我這平凡身又如何博得慷慨<br />\n<br />\n我慶幸這一生以後毫無顧慮   何用領受你允許<br />\n我怎麼可以往後退   等救援隊<br />\n若被困重災區   毅然不衰<br />\n<br />\n我要為此犧牲你為何流眼淚   何用你為我讚許<br />\n沒有掌聲如雷   只有洪水<br />\n讓我踏進方舟   錯下去<br />\n<br />\n我會為此犧牲我亦毫無畏懼   無疑這是個壯舉<br />\n我怎麼可以往後退   等救援隊<br />\n若並無情人   其實多麼鎖碎<br />\n<br />\n我要為此犧牲你為何流眼淚   前行了就別再追<br />\n就當捨身成仁   為何不對<br />\n直到直到一天   過去<br />\n<br />\n我共你始終   淡似水<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n一直以來都未物色到合適既人去錄呢兩首歌，有興趣既絲打可以試下唱，小弟感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG 改編歌詞集中討論區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/17213\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg.na.cx%2Fthread%2F17213&d=K3dCVXl4wAKZNk47p1F0uJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=5fd16f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/17213</a> <br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n希望巴打絲們多多支持小弟既 音樂x旅遊 專頁￼ ￼ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFacebook:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/aamusictravel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Faamusictravel&d=K3dCVXl4wAKZNk47p1F0uJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=13e85f29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/aamusictravel</a> <br />\nBlog: [url]<a href=\"https://aamusictravel.wordpress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamusictravel.wordpress.com&d=K3dCVXl4wAKZNk47p1F0uJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=05208e6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://aamusictravel.wordpress.com</a> [/url]<br />\nInstagram: aa.music.travel"},{"pid":"5cc1f5aff40aae993e7070bd7cd5b524a1c6d302","tid":39471,"uid":2350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc2d3de363b034a1778b737f8dc050c4da35ea1","tid":39471,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59120b426c708ed1b4b9a5e41bcd2dcd4c5a1b43","tid":39471,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7999bba69bbaae11baef99c598a4e58d79197667","tid":39471,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:18:06.000Z","msg":"好鍾意&quot;願我可以學會放低你&quot;呢首歌，鍾意到唔敢改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0560bbc086396ebcae2b6ff6b1ff247888ec3108","tid":39471,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708d5e3cb022bd01733a785fff823ff33cef2ec7","tid":39471,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好鍾意&quot;願我可以學會放低你&quot;呢首歌，鍾意到唔敢改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前細個唔識野，見有歌就改，換轉今日可能都會唔想改，好似《四季》咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb5daa52daac7d5111e7d3bc5825eabeb24da2c","tid":39471,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T09:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32489bee9594d6668942fd1b6bf034860995c4e","tid":39471,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"